OL,4,Casylum centre tensions
OL,6,FPolice chiefs will be questioned about
OL,7,Ftensions over the use of a former army
OL,8,Ftraining camp for a temporary asylum
OL,9,Faccommodation centre.
OL,11,FHundreds of people took part in a
OL,12,Fprotest in Crowborough, East Sussex,
OL,13,Fover the plans to house 540 single
OL,14,Fmale adults from the end of November
OL,15,Ffor up to a year.
OL,17,FThe Sussex Police and Crime
OL,18,FCommissioner will question officers on
OL,19,Ftheir plans to manage demonstrations
OL,20,Fand stop tensions from escalating.
