OL,6,FKaty Bourne wants to know about the
OL,7,Fimpact it will have on police
OL,8,Fresources and whether Sussex police
OL,9,Fwill need additional funding for more
OL,10,Fpatrols in the area.
OL,12,FThe meeting, which takes places on
OL,13,FThursday (20 November), is part of a
OL,14,Fregular performance review of the
OL,15,Fforce and will also address knife
OL,16,Fcrime and a recent report on child
OL,17,Fsexual exploitation and grooming gangs.
