OL,6,FPCC, Katy Bourne said: "I know that
OL,7,Fmany residents in Crowborough and the
OL,8,Fsurrounding areas are understandably
OL,9,Fconcerned about the impact this
OL,10,Fdecision may have on their community.
OL,12,F"It's vital that local people feel
OL,13,Freassured that their concerns are not
OL,14,Fonly being heard but also addressed.
