OL,6,F"As soon as I heard about the plans
OL,7,Ffor the Crowborough site, I wrote to
OL,8,Fthe Home Secretary and the Minister
OL,9,Ffor Border Security and Asylum to
OL,10,Fpoint out that the site had previously
OL,11,Fbeen deemed unsuitable by the Home
OL,12,FOffice under the previous Conservative
OL,13,FGovernment, and to articulate local
OL,14,Fresidents' dismay and anger at the
OL,15,Flack of public consultation and
OL,16,Fconcerns regarding safety."
