OL,3,CPolice chiefs to be questioned about
OL,4,Casylum centre tensions
OL,6,FHome Secretary, Shabana Mahmood has
OL,7,Funveiled her reforms to the asylum
OL,8,Fsystem, which she claimed was
OL,9,Fattracting too many applicants due to
OL,10,Fthe "comparative generosity" of the
OL,11,FUK's laws compared to Europe, amid
OL,12,Fgrowing backlash from Labour MPs.
OL,14,FBilled as the largest change to the
OL,15,FUK's system in the modern era, Home
OL,16,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood said it was
OL,17,Fnecessary to stop people "aslyum
OL,18,Fshopping" around Europe.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
