OL,3,CPolice chiefs to be questioned about
OL,4,Casylum centre tensions
OL,6,FSpeaking in the Commons soon after the
OL,7,Ffull reform package was published,
OL,8,FMahmood said: "It starts by accepting
OL,9,Fan uncomfortable truth, while asylum
OL,10,Fclaims fall across Europe, they are
OL,11,Frising here, and that is because of
OL,12,Fthe comparative generosity of our
OL,13,Fasylum offer, when compared to so many
OL,14,Fof our European neighbours.
OL,16,F"This generosity is a factor that
OL,17,Fdraws people to these shores on a path
OL,18,Fthat runs through other safe
OL,19,Fcountries."
