OL,4,Casylum centre tensions
OL,6,FShe noted the current asylum system
OL,7,F"feels out of control and unfair"
OL,8,Fsaying "the pace and scale of change
OL,9,Fhas destabilised communities, it is
OL,10,Fmaking our country a more divided
OL,11,Fplace."
OL,13,FThe government is already facing a
OL,14,Fmounting wave of discontent from its
OL,15,Fown backbenchers, with 16 coming out
OL,16,Falready against the plans.
